General.Name: Federal Mogul Izmit Piston ve Pim Uretim Tesisleri AS
General.Description: Federal-Mogul Izmit Piston Ve Pim Üretim Tesisleri A.S. manufactures and trades in pistons and pins in Turkey. The company was incorporated in 1967 and is headquartered in Kocaeli, Turkey. Federal-Mogul Izmit Piston Ve Pim Üretim Tesisleri A.S. is a subsidiary of Federal Mogul Powertrain Otomotiv A.S.
